          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-744 osc: add lru pages management - new RPC",
        "message": "LU-744 osc: add lru pages management - new RPC\n\nAdd a cache management at osc layer, this way we can control how much\nmemory can be used to cache lustre pages and avoid complex solution\nas what we did in b1_8.\n\nRight now, admins can set how much memory an OSC can cache lustre\npages. This is not perfect because an application may only access\nlimited number of OSCs in a burst read. A self-adapative algorithm\nwill be worked out to solve this issue.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I8c1f48e8f56881414617ea848a8a9a39c784ee18\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
